'''''Born in the Wrong Body''''' is an American [[television documentary]] [[Television series|series]] about [[transgender]] experiences. It premiered on April 22, 2007 on [[MSNBC]]. The second installment, "On the Edge", aired on December 28, followed by "Girls Will Be Boys" on January 20, 2008.
